2/4/05 -- First release version 0.001

Version 0.002 (2/15/05)
----------------------
Fixed near field calculation for kbc0 = 3 and kbc0 = 2 case.
Fixed far field calculations (ftfeld.c).

Version 0.004 (4/4/05)
----------------------
Fixed near field intensity calculation.
Fixed near field plotting routine to make sure minimum of 10
points inside each layer are plotted.
Added QZMR looping function.
Started working on the Makefile.


